channel.title: Some help with moparscape 3.1
channel.description:
um yeah i get a message when it trys to load it is...
sorry, an error has occured whilts loading runescape
to fix thistry the following (in order):
1:try closing all open web-browser windows and reloading 2:try clearing your web-browsers cache from tools-> internet options 3:try using a different game world 4:try rebooting your computer 5:try selecting a different version of java from the play-game menu
i tried 1, 2 and 4 but the other 2 i have no idea what it means.
hopefully someone can help.
